6
00:00:12.560 --> 00:00:17.560
It is time to put all of these insights together into a cohesive story for DataSearch.

7
00:00:17.560 --> 00:00:23.040
Specifically, we will be focusing this final chapter on building a dashboard for our client.

8
00:00:23.040 --> 00:00:23.040


9
